-- Growing Rugby's Appeal in Asia
-- B y
-- 2012-06-04T05:51:39Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-04/growing-rugby-s-appeal-in-asia.html
The sport of rugby seeks to broaden 
its appeal globally. Next year, the British Lions tackle 
Australia, and they'll stop in Hong Kong for their first-ever 
match in Asia. Paul Allen spoke to the former Australian 
captain John Eales about rugby's efforts to grow the game in 
Asia. (Source: Bloomberg)  Running Time: 03:04
 